name: When You Are Leaving
description:
Another work of calligraphy that I feel my soul in this work and I love it very much
The interesting thing is that after designing things, I always say how did I design this work? The feeling of that moment is very sacred
When someone wants to leave you alone
Everything is always said and you ask him to stay
Tell him everything
If he comes back one day, tell him not to regret why you will not accept him again
